Package: AMIM
Type: Package
Title: Compute the Adjusted Market Inefficient Measure
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given= "Vu Le", family="Tran", email= "gelotran@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3593-9611"))
Maintainer: Vu Le Tran <gelotran@gmail.com>
Description: Fast tool to calculate the Adjusted Market Inefficient Measure following Tran & Leirvik (2019) "A simple but powerful measure of market efficiency", Finance Research Letters, 29, pp.141-151. Provides rolling window estimates of the Adjusted Market Inefficient Measure for mutiple instruments simultaneously. 
